'''Micro-books''' were antique data-storage devices, essentially mechanized books. During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] delivered a shipment of pre-[[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] micro-books to the school of [[Myoris Lin]] on [[Harix]].

